description: The Fairfax County Urban Biodiversity Dashboard visualizes urban biodiversity patterns using data from the iNaturalist API. The dashboard helps track and understand wildlife patterns, habitat health, and biodiversity trends.

name: Credit-Card-Clustering-Analysis
description: This project analyzes credit card customer data using K-Medoids and Hierarchical Clustering. Visualizations and statistical evaluations assess cluster quality for insights into customer behavior.
